        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]

FROM [ParsaPooladMenus] AS [p]

    SELECT [w].[PrdFirstGroupID], [w].[FGName], [t].[WsproductSecondGroupId], [t].[Sgname], [w].[ParsaPooladMenusId]
    FROM [WSProductFirstGroup] AS [w]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] AS [WsproductSecondGroupId], [w0].[SGName] AS [Sgname], [w0].[FirstGroupId]

        WHERE [w0].[IsRemoved] IS NULL
    ) AS [t] ON [w].[PrdFirstGroupID] = [t].[FirstGroupId]

2021-06-07T18:13:24.6741424+04:30 0HM99N4IFQHH7:0000011B [INF] Executed DbCommand ("2"ms) [Parameters=[""], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [w].[ProductID], [w].[PrdPrice], [w].[PrdName], [w].[PrdInactiveInSale], [w].[RegisterDatePersian], [t0].[SGName], [t0].[c]
FROM [WSProducts] AS [w]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t].[SGName], [t].[c], [t].[PrdSecondGroupID]
    FROM (
        SELECT [w0].[SGName], 1 AS [c], [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID] ORDER BY [w0].[PrdSecondGroupID]) AS [row]
        FROM [WSProductSecondGroup] AS [w0]
    ) AS [t]
